* MOSFET CS amplifier
VDD vdd 0 DC 10.45
Vin in 0 AC 1
Cin in gate 15u
RG1 vdd gate 820k
RG2 gate 0 390k
RD vdd drain 5.6k
M1 drain gate source 0 NMOS1
RS source 0 1.5k
Cout drain out 15u
